title: Duo Queue.
body:
Looking for a Legit Duo Partner.
Someone who I can play placements, normals and ranked with.
I'll play with anyone who has a friendly attitude and who likes the game as much as me, I don't mind you playing any lanes but keep in mind, my best roles are mid and jungle. 
See you on the rift.

replies.body: add me ingame, we can do that tasty duo stuff.
